archimate:BusinessObject.name: Test Result
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
This object type corresponds to the ISA-95 object type ISA95TestResultType: "This VariableType indicates the test results." (https://reference.opcfoundation.org/ISA-95/v100/docs/7.5.4 )
OPC-10030 defines attributes of the Test Result. Further detail for Test Result information is described in https://reference.opcfoundation.org/ISA-95/v100/docs/7.3.
